tossup_question: -   –  The derivative of sine-cubed of 2 theta with respect to theta is equal to which of the following?
tossup_MCQoptions:
W) Cosine-cubed of 2 theta
X) 3 sine-squared of 2 theta
Y) 6 sine-squared of 2 theta cosine of 2 theta
Z) 6 cosine-cubed of 2 theta sine-squared of 2 theta
tossup_answer: ANSWER: Y) 6 sine-squared of 2 theta cosine of 2 theta
